MyReports - Statistic reports for MySQL Servers
===============================================

Description
-----------

This is a personal project realized in Python language and Django v1.3 web
framework. Basically consists in a MySQL variable-value collector and a
customizable report generator for one or more MySQL servers configured.


Installation
------------

1) Get the code: https://github.com/ariel17/myreports

2) Create a virtual environment for Python using virtualenv
[http://www.virtualenv.org/] and virtualenvwrapper
[http://www.doughellmann.com/projects/virtualenvwrapper/].

3) Install dependences with pip [http://www.pip-installer.org] and RRDTool
[http://oss.oetiker.ch/rrdtool/].

5) Configure settings.py using settings.example.py as base file.

6) Adjust your prefered database and sync.

7) See collector-*_call-example files for example executions.


You can always check for --help ;)

